		<span id="title-177094295" class="story-title"> <a   href="//yro.slashdot.org/story/25/04/22/191219/un-says-asian-scam-call-center-epidemic-expanding-globally-amid-political-heat">UN Says Asian Scam Call Center Epidemic Expanding Globally Amid Political Heat</a> <span class=" no extlnk"><a class="story-sourcelnk" href="https://www.theregister.com/2025/04/22/un_asian_scam_calls/"  title="External link - https://www.theregister.com/2025/04/22/un_asian_scam_calls/" target="_blank"> (theregister.com) </a></span></span>

		
		
