		<!-- comment bubble -->
		
			<span class="comment-bubble"><a href="//yro.slashdot.org/story/25/04/22/191219/un-says-asian-scam-call-center-epidemic-expanding-globally-amid-political-heat#comments" title="">44</a></span>
		
