I don't get the texts anymore for some reason; I think my number is on a "do not call" list used by these outfits. Before that, I got a lot of photos from "Chinese women". At one point, a "Japanese woman" and I fell in love at first text. I typically immediately require that they call me "sir" to test the response, and then engage in depth. They either don't get the jokes or don't care or I don't know how to explain it, but they persist, potential</div>
